A '''Dantooine flapjack''' was foodstuff from [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]]. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] crew of the shuttle ''[[Bonderium]]'' mentioned this dish in an analogy to help the chef droid [[L9-G8]] fly the shuttle in combat against [[Teehl]]'s pirate ship ''[[Grasp]]''.

